                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7722" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0523</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2356 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">捷“足”先登：爱踢客高素质教练团队的创新人才激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The first to go in the football industry: Innovative talent motivation for a highly qualified coaching team of Hi Kicker</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钱婧，吴榕，牛文卓，屈逸，王斌，张伟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京爱踢客体育文化有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">高素质教练团队；人才激励；足球培训；爱踢客</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">High quality coach teams; Talent motivation; Football training; Hi Kicker</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在体育强国战略和全民健身氛围的背景之下，近年来足球培训行业逐步成为消费体育行业的“香饽饽”。成立于2014年的北京爱踢客体育文化有限责任公司积极布局青少年足球培训产业，其教练团队一直在训练中不断成长。本案例描述了爱踢客打造高素质教练团队，进而在行业中“捷‘足’先登”，成为北京市规模最大的青少年足球培训俱乐部的发展历程。随着组织规模逐步扩大，爱踢客如何吸引人才并设立教练团队的聘用标准？如何激励专业的全职和兼职教练？在初步形成团队后，如何通过设计合理的教练员培训体系和晋升通道来留住人才并激发价值。通过对爱踢客创新人才激励实践方法的剖析，该案例旨在帮助学员理解教育培训行业人才激励的特征及有效途径，并且进一步思考教育培训企业如何用创新的激励手段建设人才梯队。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, the Chinese government has put forward &quot;Outline for Building a Leading Sports Nation&quot; and the national fitness campaign. In this context, the football training has gained attention and popularity in the consumer sports industry. Founded in 2014, Hi Kicker is actively involved in the youth football training related industry and its coaching team has continued to grow. This case describes the development of Hi Kicker&#39;s highly qualified coach team, which makes it become the largest youth football training club in Beijing, analyses the company&#39;s management practices of motivating professional full-time and part-time coaches, designing a reasonable training system and promotion pathway for the coaching team. By depicting Hi Kiker&#39;s innovative approach to talent motivation, the case aims to help participants understand the characteristics and effective ways to motivate talent in the education and training industry, and to further consider how education and training companies can use innovative motivational tools to build their talent pipeline.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自我决定理论的三种动机需求；社会网络视角下中小企业人才吸引模式；混合雇佣理论；基于胜任力的培训设计；多通道晋升机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
